= Twitter avi

This application is a demo application to study Ruby on Rails.

The initial development is following the Ruby on Rails tutorial
http://ruby.railstutorial.org/

Then the project is developped following the twitter idea in order to increase my RoR level.

= Completed

- Ruby on Rails tutorial implementation completed with the exercices.
- Added reply to messages.
=> TODO : Add more Javascript to provide more dynamism on the site.
